descriptionHtml:
[b]Nefertari Vivi[/b] is the princess of [url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Alabasta]Alabasta[/url]. She is the daughter of [url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Nefertari_Cobra]Nefertari Cobra[/url] and [url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Nefertari_Titi]Nefertari Titi[/url]. She was one of the main antagonists of the [url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Reverse_Mountain_Arc]Reverse Mountain Arc[/url] under the Baroque Works codename [b]Miss Wednesday[/b],[url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi#cite_note-Miss_Wednesday_intro-1][2][/url] but she ended up traveling with the [url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates]Straw Hat Pirates[/url] for most of the [url=http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Alabasta_Saga]Alabasta Saga[/url] after revealing herself to be a spy plotting against Baroque Works. She has not been featured in the main story since the Straw Hats left Alabasta but has occasionally been shown to be keeping track of their progress.

Download instructions:
Download the file and open the saved game.
Load the save, use shadowracemenu and then press F5 to save the face, after that press F9 to apply it.
Tip: Only use for ningheim for it to work properly.
Required:
Sevenbase body replacer. Ningheim race. Coverwomen.  SG female eyebrows. SG female textures renewal. KS hairdos renewal. [b]Alternate Start - Live Another Life by [b]Arthmoor.[/b][/b][quote](Leave a comment if the saved game doesn't work.)[/quote]
author: Mugiwara
